 Delta State Governor, Senator Dr. Ifeanyi Okowa Thursday inaugurated the newly appointed Senior Political Adviser, Hon. Chief Funkekeme Solomon. The ceremony took place in Asaba. Funkekeme Solomon who was a former Deputy Speaker of the Delta State House of Assembly, former Commissioner for Works and Director-General of the PDP 2019 Campaign Council was appointed Senior Political Adviser on May 31, 2019. The post Okowa Inaugurates Funkekeme As Senior POLAD Source: Independent